org.osate.ge.ui

Class UiBusinessObjectSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osate.ge.ui.UiBusinessObjectSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectSelection

    public class UiBusinessObjectSelection
extends java.lang.Object
implements BusinessObjectSelection
    Implementation of BusinessObjectSelection which uses the action executor of the active editor to perform modifications if it is available. Otherwise it uses the ActionService service registered with the workbench.
    Since:
    2.0

                                       java.util.function.Function<BusinessObjectContext,T> bocToBoToModifyMapper,
                                       java.util.function.BiConsumer<T,BusinessObjectContext> modifier)
        Description copied from interface: BusinessObjectSelection
        After filtering business object contexts using the specified filter, calls the specified modifier for each business object provided by the bocToBoToModifyMapper. Also provides the business object context. The business objects contained in the business object context must not be modified.
        Specified by:
        modify in interface BusinessObjectSelection
        Parameters:
        label - is a description of the modification.
        bocFilter - is the filter for business object contexts. Only business object contexts which pass the filter are modified.
        bocToBoToModifyMapper - is a function which returns the object which should be modified based on a business object context.
        modifier - is a function which is passed the object to be modified and the business object context.
